  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Manager (ID)/ Project Director (ID)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Project Manager (ID)/ Project Director (ID)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>Overall in-charge of the project.</p>\n<p>Liaise closely with Clients/Designers and provide the project team expertise and supervision.</p>\n<p>Verify and confirm quotations from Suppliers/Contractors (especially indent items).</p>\n<p>Proactively manage changes in project scope, identify potential crisis, and devise contingency plans.</p>\n<p>Ensure all plans/documents to Landlords/Local Authorities are approved prior to commencement of work.</p>\n<p>Conduct site marking/inspection prior to commencement of work.</p>\n<p>Conduct regular site meeting.</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Degree in Architecture, Construction or relevant disciplines.</p>\n<p>Minimum 5 years local experience in large-scale projects (commercial / space / retail / F&amp;B).</p>\n<p>Good project management and site co-ordination skills.</p>\n<p>Proficient in MS Office (Words/Excel/PowerPoint).</p>",
